Paper: hep-th/9402011

Date: 1994-02-02

Title: A simple construction of elliptic $R$-matrices

Comments: 6 pages

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 32 (1994) 167-171

We show that Belavin's solutions of the quantum Yang--Baxter equation can beobtained by restricting an infinite $R$-matrix to suitable finite dimensionalsubspaces. This infinite $R$-matrix is a modified version of theShibukawa--Ueno $R$-matrix acting on functions of two variables.